      en: 'fireworks-tech-graph: AI Diagram Generator for Docs and Architecture'
    },
    stars: '⭐ 3.1k',
    summary: {
      zh: '一个 Claude Code 技能，用于生成生产级 SVG+PNG 技术图表。它直指 AI 开发流程中的可视化表达痛点。',
      en: 'A Claude Code skill for generating production-grade SVG and PNG technical diagrams, directly addressing visualization bottlenecks in AI-native workflows.'
    },
    href: 'https://github.com/yizhiyanhua-ai/fireworks-tech-graph'
  },
  {
    icon: '🚀',
    title: {
      zh: 'codeburn：AI 编码成本追踪 TUI 仪表板',
      en: 'codeburn: TUI Dashboard for AI Coding Cost Tracking'
    },
    stars: '⭐ 1.9k',
    summary: {
      zh: '通过交互式终端仪表板追踪 token 使用与成本，说明“AI 开发成本治理”正在成为新基础设施。',
      en: 'An interactive terminal dashboard for tracking token usage and spend, showing how AI cost governance is becoming a new layer of infrastructure.'
    },
    href: 'https://github.com/AgentSeal/codeburn'
  },
  {
    icon: '💡',
    title: {
      zh: 'MOSS-TTS-Nano：能跑在 CPU 上的轻量语音模型',
      en: 'MOSS-TTS-Nano: A Lightweight Speech Model That Runs on CPU'
    },
    stars: '⭐ 1.1k',
    summary: {
      zh: '0.1B 参数的多语言语音生成模型，突出信号是“小模型 + 边缘部署”正在打开更低成本的 AI 产品形态。',
      en: 'A 0.1B multilingual speech model whose real signal is the rise of small models and edge deployment as a lower-cost product path.'
    },
    href: 'https://github.com/OpenMOSS/MOSS-TTS-Nano'
